text: Tarakan is an island city in North Kalimantan, Indonesia. Tarakan may also refer to: * Mount Tarakan, a volcano in the Halmahera islands * Battle of Tarakan (1942), a battle in World War II * Battle of Tarakan (1945), a battle in World War II * HMAS Tarakan (L 129), a heavy landing craft commissioned in 1973 * HMAS Tarakan (L3017), a tank landing ship commissioned in 1946 ==See also== *Taraqan
title: Tarakan (disambiguation)
